<LI><A HREF="#ByMail">Obtaining the Software by Electronic Mail</A>
<LI><A HREF="#ByInst">Obtaining the Software Within Silicon Graphics</A>
</UL>

All the HylaFAX documentation is online on the WWW.
<A HREF="install-source.html">Installation (source distribution)</A>
describes how to unpack and install the source distribution images.
<A HREF="install-binary.html">Installation (binary distribution)</A>
describes what to do with a binary distribution.
The <A HREF="index.html">HylaFAX home page</A> is the place to go
for <EM>all</EM> the HylaFAX documentation.
<P>
There are several mailing lists for HylaFAX users; you can subscribe
through <A HREF="mailing-lists.html">this online form</A>.

